name: Level Uncomplete
description:
Oh no, Reed Hatboy has dropped his phone in Level 0. Even worse, he is stuck in level 1 until he touches the orb at the end of the level. Even worse than that, every time he dies he progresses to the next level and grows further away from his precious phone.

Jump and dodge through a facility full of evil robots and deadly acid and get the orbs to go back or uncomple the previous level.  A and D or Arrow keys to move and space to jump. Good luck, you’ll need it!

Thanks to pzUH for the character, robot, tileset, and orb, to CTatz for making the phone, and to https://cooltext.com/ for the font I used. Also, thanks to NotEuclid for helping me make the songs for the game. And thanks to you for checking out this game.
